title: Dilwala KANNADA - PRK Group's.VOB
description:
Dilwala is a romantic thriller, which is based on the life of college going youths.It is a Second Premaloka.Premaloka , which was released in the year 1987. Dilwala will be admired by the youths of this generation, like how Premaloka was admired then.Dilwala has been made with a limited budget. It features Sumanth Shailendra and Radhika Pandit in the lead roles.
